
	
	To: Testing, Support
	Date: 12-12-88
	From: Duncan
	Re: Zork0/MacII startup bug

	Description: 
	Game hangs while loading.

	Conditions:
	Happens only on a color MacII equipped with
	- a single disk drive (forcing swaps between game and
	  System disks during loading)
	- System version 5.0 or 6.0

	Fix:
	Startup the MacII with System 6.0.1, 6.0.2, or higher.
